    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tidyr,
    dplyr
Imports: gtools,
         ggplot2,
         mvtnorm
URL: https://github.com/dm13450/dirichletprocess
BugReports: https://github.com/dm13450/dirichletprocess/issues
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
